text:
Cooper Ave., east from 66th Place, showing at the left foreground the Kolyer House No 66-33 Cooper Ave. At the right is the Mt. Carmel and Evergreens Cemetery.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

Cooper Ave., east of 66th Place (formerly Gamma Place) to 67th Place (formerly Alpha Place) showing in the foreground the Denton House, formerly numbered 2709 and which is now. No 66-53. The three storied structure in the center of view, is at the N.E. corner of Cooper Ave. and 67th Street (formerly Beta Street).

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
